%h1 Upload a demo.

%p Upload a warsow demo (*.wd9, *.wd10 or *.wd11) or a defrag demo (*.dm_68).

- form_for :demofile, :url => { :action => :create }, :html => { :multipart => true } do |f|
  %p
    = error_messages_for 'demofile'
  %p
    = f.file_field :uploaded_data, :size => 50
  %p
    = submit_tag :Upload

  - unless @valid
    %p.error
      If you have trouble with uploading demos and you want me to check it,
      %br
      please upload this demo with a good error report to
      = link_to "stuff upload.", new_stuff_path
      Thanks.

